synopsis.text: Squad Jam, the intense team battle royale tournament in Sword Art Online Alternative: Gun Gale Online, has reached its thrilling climax! Unfortunately, Pitohui missed the action-packed event. To fill her in on the details, M provides a captivating play-by-play commentary as they watch the replay together, revealing the challenges faced by the participants and the triumphant victors of the tournament. Prepare to dive back into the world of Gun Gale Online and witness the excitement of Squad Jam unfold!
